{0 Clauses And Triples}

The reduction is expressed in two layers.

{1 Generated Clauses}

{!module-SpecV2.GeneratedClauses} defines semantic clauses over one tick
context:

- initialization clauses;
- propagation clauses;
- safety clauses excluding dangerous steps.

{1 Relational Triples}

{!module-SpecV2.RelationalTriples} packages the generated clauses into local
proof obligations. Triples are either attached to the initial tick or to one
transition label.
